      "role": "user",
      "content": "fair enough. but if you look at how much these companies actually invest in r&d, it feels like they're the ones actually driving the tech forward. if the gov starts picking winners and losers via these investigations, doesn't that just create a more stagnant environment in the long run? seems like a risky move to go against the very engines of progress.",
